{
  "chapter": 3,
  "chapter_summary": "楚留香与胡铁花随李玉函夫妇返回拥翠山庄，途中讨论柳无眉武功来历，楚留香对其师承产生怀疑。抵达开封后，柳无眉夜间突发怪疾，痛苦不堪，楚留香推测她可能中了剧毒而非患病。突然有人以\"暴雨梨花钉\"偷袭楚留香，幸得宿雁惊起才侥幸避开。楚留香追击刺客未果，胡铁花捡到银匣子。二人研究暴雨梨花钉的构造与威力，确认此物为暗器之王，天下无人能闪避其发射。楚留香感叹刺客轻功已与无花不相上下，胡铁花的酒杯中被人下毒，幸而楚留香及时发现。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蓉儿她们是怎么到了拥翠山庄的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我现在可要卖个关子，反正你见到苏姑娘后，就会知道的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你眼光实在不错，李玉函夫妇使的的确是'金丝绵掌'，方仙客素无传人，却和李观鱼是生死之交，所以就将一身绝技传给他的儿子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "令人想不到的是，昔日的第一剑客，如今竟已成了废人，武林前辈日渐凋零，实在令人可悲可叹。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "好在他还有这么一个好儿子，'九九八十一式凌风剑'，再加上'金丝绵掌'，拥翠山庄还怕不在他手里更发扬光大。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "依我看来，柳无眉的武功非但不在她夫婿之下，而且还像是比李玉函高些，尤其是她的轻功身法，更高出许多。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "三大武林世家的绝技俱是传媳不传女，她既然做了李观鱼的媳妇，武功自然也绝不会差的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她嫁到李家去，绝不会超过十年，而这种武林世家的子弟，大多从三五岁时就开始练武，李玉函自也不会例外。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，我看他身上最少也有着十年的苦功夫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "既然如此，柳无眉的武功就不该比李玉函高，除非她的娘家也是武林名家，但环顾天下，又有几个人教徒弟能比李观鱼教得好呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你莫非又在猜疑人家的来历了?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我几次想探问她的师承，她总是岔了开去，由此可见，她绝不会是四大帮、七大派的门下，我也想不出当今武林中有什么姓柳的前辈高人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "无论如何，你总不能怀疑李观鱼的媳妇会是画眉鸟吧!何况，就算她是画眉鸟又怎样?画眉鸟对咱们可只有好处，没有过节，连我这条命，还是画眉鸟救回来的哩!她若是画眉鸟，我只有更感激她。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你杀了我吧!杀了我吧!",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yu_han",
      "speaker_name": "李玉函",
      "listener": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "text": "忍耐些，忍耐些，莫吵醒了别人。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_wu_mei",
      "speaker_name": "柳无眉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我实在忍耐不住了，与其这样受苦，倒不如死了的好。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "莫非她忽然得了急病?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这病只怕并不是突发的，而是宿疾，而且还必定时常发作，所以连他们的佣人都已听惯了，否则怎会一个个躲在屋里不出来。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这痛苦一发作想必就很厉害，否则像柳无眉这样的人绝不会喊出声来的，却不知她生的究竟是什么病呢?",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她平时看来倒也和常人无异，想不到一发作就如此可怕，我看，她这也许并不是病，而是中了什么极厉害的毒。",
      "tone": "沉吟",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "毒?她若中了毒，李观鱼为何不想法子救她?久闻李观鱼医道极高明，拥翠山庄中来往的又都是前辈高人，方仙客更是解毒的名家，这许多人难道都无法解得了她的毒?都眼见着她受苦么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你为什么不进去瞧瞧，或许你能解得了她的毒也未可知。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "柳无眉是个很好强的女人，必定不愿意被人看到她如此狼狈的模样，有什么话，还是等到明天再说吧!",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "老臭虫，小心了，这好像是'暴雨梨花钉'。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "小胡，是你?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你现在怎地也和我一样，连招呼也不打就出手了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "我见到你手上有银光闪动，自然认定了你必定是那发暗器的人，又谁想得到这东西竟会到了你手上呢?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这你都想不到么?我三拳两脚，将那小子打得狼狈而逃，这东西自然就到了我的手上了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "真的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "假的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实我也知道你是万万追不着他的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我追不上他还有理可说，轻功天下第一的楚香帅，怎么追了半天，也将他的人追丢了呢?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若不是这场雾，我也许还能追得上他的，但此人的轻功也实在不弱，我追出墙外时，他的人已掠出去有四五十丈了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "就那么一眨眼的功夫，他已掠出去四五十丈，如此说来，他的轻功岂非比李玉函夫妻还高么?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只怕是要高出一筹。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "比我呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你若少喝些酒，他轻功也许不如你的，但现在……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "现在又怎样?现在我难道连李玉函夫妻都不如么?",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你用不着回答我的这句话，也免得我听了伤心。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "其实你的轻功和李玉函夫妻、一点红、南宫灵都差不多，都已可算是一等一的功夫，但这人的轻功却已和无花不相上下，这次若不是我亲眼见到无花的咽喉已被利箭穿过，只怕又要以为是无花复活了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此说来，江湖中能有他这样轻功的人并不多，是么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "实在不多。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你为什么总是会遇见一些厉害的对头?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你手上这东西是哪里来的?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "捡来的，上面还刻着字，你瞧瞧认不认得?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是小篆。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "明明是杀人的利器，却偏偏要文绉绉的刻些人家不认得的字在上面，这简直好像明明是妓女，却偏偏要穿七八条裤子。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这倒并非是故意卖弄，只因这暗器实在是件古物，而且还是个不会武功的人制成的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不错，我也听说过这'暴雨梨花钉'的掌故，但上面刻的字究竟是在说什么呢?",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上面刻的是：出必见血，空回不祥。急中之急，暗器之王。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "文人都会说大话，看来果然不错。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这倒也不是他在故意说大话骇人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此暗器制作之精巧，发射力量之猛，实在不愧为'暗器之王'四字，当今武林中几件有名的暗器，和此物一比，速度至少要相差两成，而暗器一物，决胜伤人，就在一刹那间，纵然是毫厘之差，也差得太多了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "此物难道比石观音所制的针筒还强得多么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "石观音那针筒射出来的毒针虽急，但你等它发射后再闪避，也还来得及的，而这'暴雨梨花钉'发射后，天下却无一人能闪得开。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "可是你方才却闪避开了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那实在是运气，只因我在它还未发射前，就有警觉，但纵然如此，那人发射的位置若再近几尺，我还是避不开的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "如此说来，这暗器岂非珍贵已极?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在武林中人眼里看来，它实在可说是无价之宝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "既是如此，那人为什么要将它抛在地上呢?他既然有那么高的功夫，难道连这小匣子都拿不稳么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这的确是件很奇怪的事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "咱们穷追了半夜，却连人家的影子也未见着，再不快喝杯酒，我简直就要活活气死了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你迟些喝酒也一定死不了的，咱们还是先到院子里瞧瞧那些'暴雨梨花钉'是否还在那里。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "你看他发射暗器的地方，距离这里有多远?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "只怕有四五丈。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这些梨花钉在四五丈外射过来，居然还能直没入土，这种暗器的力量是何等强猛，你就可想而知。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我真想将这匣子拆开来看看，看看里面的机簧究竟是怎么做出来的，这匣子简直就好像有二十七个小鬼在拉着弓弦似的。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么小的一根针也能钉入地下，我若非亲眼瞧见，随便怎么我也不会相信。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就因为它的速度，所以力量才大。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "speaker_name": "胡铁花",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这小小一根钉打在地上，便直没入土，若是打在人身上，那还得了……我一定要将它们装回去，试试它们射出来时究竟有多快?",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_hu_tie_hua",
      "text": "此物看来极为锋利，你要小心了。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 3,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    }
